---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Why we built the Vegan Pet Directory — a curated catalog of plant-based pet brands by VIRIDA."
>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-display font-extrabold text-leaf-900">Why this directory exists</h1>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-lg text-leaf-800 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        Vegan pet parents face a frustrating problem: there's no single place to
        discover trustworthy plant-based food, treats, and supplements for their
        animals. Information is scattered across Reddit threads, Facebook groups,
        and outdated blog posts.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>The Vegan Pet Directory</strong> exists to fix that. We catalog
        every legitimate vegan pet brand we can find — globally — and check the
        facts so you don't have to.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-leaf-900 pt-4">How brands get listed</h2>
      <p>
        We list brands that meet three criteria:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>Products are 100% plant-based (no meat, dairy, or animal by-products).</li>
        <li>The brand is currently active and shipping to at least one country.</li>
        <li>The website is live and the company is contactable.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-leaf-900 pt-4">Who runs this</h2>
      <p>
        This directory is published by{' '}
        <a href="https://virida.pet" class="text-leaf-600 underline">VIRIDA</a> —
        a Taiwan-based vegan pet brand making a 10-in-1 plant-based dog chew. We
        sell our own product, but we list every competitor we know of, with no
        paid placements. The directory is open-source and built on Astro.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-leaf-900 pt-4">Submit a brand</h2>
      <p>
        Know a vegan pet brand we missed? Email{' '}
        <a href="mailto:hello@virida.pet" class="text-leaf-600 underline">
          hello@virida.pet
        </a>{' '}
        with the brand name, website, and 1-2 sentences about what they make.
        We'll review and add it within 7 days.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
